ent from thew face-to-face class.</span></span>", "授業外学習2": "<span times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"=\"roman',serif;background-image:initial;background-position:initial;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;'\" style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:;\">Students are expected to do 60-90 minutes of outside study outside per class session.</span>"}, "評価": {"教科書/Required texts0": ["No textbook. Learning materials will be provided by the instructor.\nStudents will be expected to access online English language news media, therefore a notebook PC is recommended.&nbsp;"], "学位授与の方針との関連Relationship to Diploma Policy0": ["Each subject is placed on the curriculum based on the Diploma Policy (DP) and Curriculum Policy (CP) established by each faculty and graduate school.&nbsp;\nBy studying this subject with the DP and CP in mind, you will develop the abilities expected by each faculty and graduate school.&nbsp;\nThe DP, CP and curriculum table (list of subjects, etc.) of each faculty and graduate school are posted in the link below, so please use it as a reference for your study plan.\nhttps://kwic.kwansei.ac.jp/cabinet/reference?typeCd=0&amp;cabinetId=557&amp;directLink=1\n*This is a link to kwic (only current students can view it)."], "成績評価Grading0": ["種別　Type備考　Note", "割合　Percentage", "評価基準等　Grading Criteria etc."], "成績評価Grading1": ["その他／Others (99)", "100 %", "Final Test 10%, Midterm Project 20%, Final Project 20%, Discussions 15%, Participation 20%, Flex Activities 10%, Class notebook 5%"], "成績評価Grading2": ["備考　Note 出席、遅刻の制度については以下URL先をご確認ください。/ Please refer to the following URL for details regarding the attendance and tardiness policy.https://kwic.kwansei.ac.jp/cabinet/area/detail?areaId=7144&am